This paper deals with landmark localization, which is a subfield of computer vision. The paper proposes a new objective function for training deep learning models for landmark localization, which is likely to be of interest to researchers in computer vision and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Other possible sub-categories include cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
